# GitHub owners/orgs to list in the picker, one per line. Lines starting with # are ignored.
# Copy to ${XDG_CONFIG_HOME:-~/.config}/zj/orgs (or set $ZJ_ORGS_FILE).
#
# Each entry is a GitHub login — a user or an organization. zj fetches every
# repo owned by these logins in a single GitHub GraphQL call (via gh) and shows
# each as `gh:owner/repo` (green). Selecting one clones it into $ZJ_REPOS_DIR
# (default ~/projects) if not already present, then opens a zellij session
# there named after the repo.
#
# Requires `gh` to be installed and authenticated (`gh auth login`).

kjaymiller
zellij-org
